title: Week 9 Waivers 2022
description:
Field Yates and Stephania Bell recap a spooky MNF and give injury updates before going through the fringe starters in fantasy you can trust in your lineup for the rest of the season. Plus, Eric Moody joins the show to discuss the players you have to add for Week 9.
